{"tid":1762482,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭民望淨值再創新低 82%市民反對出任特首","createTime":"2019-11-29T15:23:15.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-30T02:00:49.000Z","uid":212626,"like":34,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cee1e95621651daefd5f8582c143d61aa93a88ed","tid":1762482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:23:15.000Z","msg":"香港民意研究所今日發佈最新特首及政府民望數字。特首林鄭月娥最新評分為 19.7 分，<span style=\"color: red;\">其支持率為 11 %，反對率為 82 %</span>，民望淨值較兩周前再跌一個百分點，<span style=\"color: red;\">為負 72 個百分點</span>，再創上任以來及歷屆特首的新低。<br />\n<br />\n香港民意研究計劃前身為香港大學民意研究計劃，民研計劃於 11 月中由真實訪問員以隨機抽樣電話訪問方式，分別成功訪問了 1008 名和 519 名香港居民。特首林鄭月娥最新評分為 19.7 分，較上次調查微升 0.2 分；支持率為 11 %，反對率為 82 %，民望淨值較兩周前再跌一個百分點，為負 72 個百分點，再創上任以來及歷屆特首的新低。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">特區政府最新滿意率則為 11%，不滿率為77%，滿意率淨值為負 66 個百分點</span>，即整體上介乎「幾不滿」及「好不滿」之間。<span style=\"color: red;\">政府信任程度方面，最新的信任比率為 23%，不信任比率為 64%</span>，信任淨值為負 41 個百分點，即整體上接近「幾不信任」。<br />\n<br />\n至於對現時經濟，民生及政治狀況的滿意程度，最新滿意率分別為 20%、17% 及 4%，滿意淨值就分別為負 37、負 52 及負 79 個百分點。<br />\n<br />\n施政報告方面，施政報告發表一個月後的次輪跟進調查顯示，市民對施政報告的評價與報告發表一兩天後的首輪跟進調查結果相若，<span style=\"color: red;\">滿意率淨值為負 66 個百分點，滿意度評分則為 23.2 分，兩者分別再創 1997 年和 1999 年有紀錄以來新低</span>。而市民對特首施政方針的評價亦首輪跟進調查時相若，滿意率淨值為負 70 個百分點，亦再創 1998 年有紀錄以來新低。<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林鄭民望淨值再創新低-82-市民反對出任特首/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E6%B7%A8%E5%80%BC%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-82-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%2F&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbYytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=a552d8c7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%9E%97%E9%84%AD%E6%B0%91%E6%9C%9B%E6%B7%A8%E5%80%BC%E5%86%8D%E5%89%B5%E6%96%B0%E4%BD%8E-82-%E5%B8%82%E6%B0%91%E5%8F%8D%E5%B0%8D%E5%87%BA%E4%BB%BB%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96%2F&h=3b7fbf77\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/林鄭民望淨值再創新低-82-市民反對出任特首/</a>"},{"pid":"de47e517f42e767bdc80987371b326525f728e55","tid":1762482,"uid":219010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩先係光明頂聽到 就見到你出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b24c1977a2b5bdf462fec2baddaf6419a80bdfb","tid":1762482,"uid":301820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:24:43.000Z","msg":"點解佢仲未落台架，真係兩制就一早消失左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f2ecf21d8af38b18314e381b6443649bea3e597","tid":1762482,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"de47e517f42e767bdc80987371b326525f728e55","tid":1762482,"uid":219010,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:23:55.000Z","msg":"岩岩先係光明頂聽到 就見到你出po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:24:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a76ef7dd2c106f41fa641977453ea575297730a","tid":1762482,"uid":273703,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:25:32.000Z","msg":"打大學都做得出，未死已經益左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a875d0eb2800aeb852808fef1491eea19703ea0","tid":1762482,"uid":53003,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:25:37.000Z","msg":"林奠勁過曾暗拳，真係視民望如浮雲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"73121e517b7ef85422d6e47b27789c12a381eed1","tid":1762482,"uid":212626,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T15:26:16.000Z","msg":"又破紀錄兼攞第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c9ffaabf76cd1385b2f140ad4ba1c9c5a3da2784","ti